data.description: This home welcomes you with its huge, vaulted ceiling, great room, and open floor plan. Perfect for entertaining! With its spacious kitchen and newer high-end stainless-steel appliances, newer cabinets, granite countertops and backsplash. This home provides 3 bedrooms with larger closets and 2 full bathrooms. There are so many features to this home that cannot be missed. Everything is newer in the last few years - flooring throughout the entire property, HVAC, roof, vinyl siding, gutters, and downspouts. This place even comes with a large shed with electricity in it for your ''Do-It-Yourself'' projects. There is nothing to do here but move in and make it your own! This property also might qualify for lender grants to assist with down payment!
